        "created_at": "2016-02-05T17:08:10.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I am trying to decide which bottle to open next week.</p>\n<p>Would love to get any thoughts on:</p>\n<ol>\n<li>What is drinking better now;</li>\n<li>What will benefit more from some additional bottle age;</li>\n<li>Amount and type of decant.</li>\n</ol>\n<p>Thanks in advance!</p>\n<p>Tom</p>",
