        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/b/b487fb/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2016-02-05T17:16:14.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Had both in 2015 and to me the Dark Blossom was drinking better.  I think the Five Shooter will benefit more from additional age.</p>\n<p>I normally decant SQNs for a couple of hours, and would do so with either of these.</p>",
